======================================================
INSTALLATION
======================================================
1. Unpack the stingray folder and contents in the appropriate modules directory 
   of your Drupal installation.  Normally sites/all/modules/
   
2. Enable the stingray module on the Modules admin page (admin/build/modules)

3. You will also need a license to use Riverbed's Stingray Traffic Manager Software.
   See  http://http://www.riverbed.com.

======================================================
USAGE
======================================================
  The Refresh Tool tab is found at, admin/settings/stingray/refresh.  It is 
  part of the admin interface for this module.  From here you can list
  several paths to be cleared.

